snippet.title: Quantum Lake Preview
snippet.description:
Available for iOS and Android.

Quantum lake is a mesmerizing voyage through mysterious labyrinths in outer space.

Drive your cosmic fish shoals across 25 different scenarios of growing complexity, avoiding your enemies and reaching for the energy crystals. 

Collect as many coins as possible and choose between 5 different cosmic fish species: Quantum, Gamma Ray, Proton, Electron and Plutonium, each with different abilities.

Avoid electric fields and take advantage of the wormholes to teleport into different areas of the labyrinth, but mind your many enemies: like matter and anti-matter, bright and dark fishes will annihilate themselves upon contact. 

Quantum Lake is a game designed and developed by Damiano Gui. Music and sound effects by Eric Matyas.
